type=8&no=44|title=JC & Associates Communications, Inc.-case studies|accessdate=14 July 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150715023425/http://www.jca.com.tw/en/portfolio_page.php?type=8&no=44|archivedate=15 July 2015}}</ref>\n\nThe Audi A8 3.0 TFSI quattro (290PS) was used in [[Transporter: The Series]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.autonet.com.tw/cgi-bin/view.cgi?/news/2011/7/b1070283.ti+a2+a3+a4+a5+b1+/news/2011/7/b1070283+/car/A20060002+b3+d6+c1+c2+c3+e1+e2+e3+e5+f1|title=AutoNet \u6c7d\u8eca\u65e5\u5831\uff1a\u6bba\u9032\u5c0f\u87a2\u5e55\uff0cAUDI A8\u7e7c\u7e8c\u64d4\u4efb\u300c\u73a9\u547d\u5feb\u905e\u300d\u4e3b\u89d2\u5ea7\u99d5|publisher=|accessdate=14 July 2015}}</ref>\n\nAudi S8 was used in [[Avengers: Age of Ultron]].<ref>[https://www.autoblog.com/2015/05/03/audi-s8-stan-lee-cameo-avengers-age-ultron-video/ Audi S8 makes cameo in commercial about cameos with Stan Lee]</ref>\n\nAudi A8 was used in [[Spider-Man: Homecoming]].<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=km3TGBPo_Jc/ Audi S8 makes cameo in commercial about cameos with Stan Lee]</ref>\n\n=== 2013 model year update ===\nEarly German A8 models include 3.0 TFSI quattro (290PS), 4.0 TFSI quattro (420PS), 3.0 TDI (204PS), 3.0 TDI quattro (250PS), 3.0 TDI clean diesel quattro (250PS), 4.2 TDI quattro (350PS), A8 L W12 quattro (500PS), A8 hybrid 2.0 TFSI. Early German A8 L Security models include 4.0 TFSI quattro, W12 6.3 FSI quattro.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.audi-mediaservices.com/publish/ms/content/en/public/pressemitteilungen/2012/09/27/audi_a8__a8_l_und.standard.gid-oeffentlichkeit.html|title=Audi MediaCenter|work=Audi MediaCenter|accessdate=14 July 2015}}</ref>\n\nThe updated A8 uses LED headlight technology, with automatic high beam lighting, [[Osram]] supplies the LEDs while [[Hella (company)|Hella]] supplies the headlamp itself.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.autonews.com/article/20130915/OEM06/309169996/osram-youll-see-more-led-headlights#axzz2f47AV8Ac|title=Osram: You'll see more LED headlights|work=Automotive News|accessdate=14 July 2015}}</ref>\n\nEarly US models include the A8(L) 3.0 TFSI quattro (333PS), the A8(L) 4.0 TFSI quattro, the S8 4.0 TFSI quattro and the A8 L W12 6.3 FSI quattro. The A8 3.0 TFSI quattro and A8 4.0 TFSI quattro replaced the A8 4.2 FSI quattro.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.autoblog.com/2012/07/20/audi-adds-420-hp-4-0t-v8-to-a8-upgraded-3-0l-tdi-to-q7-for-2013/|title=Audi adds 420-HP 4.0T V8 to A8, upgraded 3.0L TDI to Q7 for 2013|author=Steven J. Ewing|work=Autoblog|accessdate=14 July 2015}}</ref> The A8 3.0 TDI clean diesel quattro (240PS) was unveiled at the 2012 L.A. Auto Show, and was set to go on sale in Spring 2013 as a 2014 model year vehicle.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.autoblog.com/2012/11/19/audi-confirms-four-new-tdi-diesel-models-headed-for-us/|title=Audi confirms four new TDI diesel models headed for US|author=Seyth Miersma|work=Autoblog|accessdate=14 July 2015}}</ref> The A8 L 3.0 TDI clean diesel quattro (240PS) was set to go on sale in Spring 2013 on sale as a 2014 model year vehicle.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.autoblog.com/2013/01/31/audi-prices-2014-a8l-tdi-from-82-500/|title=Audi prices 2014 A8L TDI from $82,500*|author=Steven J. Ewing|work=Autoblog|accessdate=14 July 2015}}</ref>\n\nChinese models include the A8L 30 FSI (204PS), the A8L 40 hybrid, the A8L 45 TFSI quattro (290PS), the A8L 55 TFSI quattro (333PS), the A8L W12 FSI quattro and the S8 4.0 TFSI quattro.<ref>[http://www.audi.cn/etc/medialib/ngw/cn/1_0_model/pdf.Par.0068.File.pdf/w12.pdf Audi A8L W12 (2012.10)]</ref><ref>[http://www.audi.cn/etc/medialib/ngw/cn/1_0_model/pdf.Par.0084.File.pdf/a8l_hybrid.pdf?frontend-debug=true Audi A8L hybrid (2013.06)]</ref><ref>[http://www.audi.cn/etc/medialib/ngw/cn/1_0_model/pdf.Par.0067.File.pdf/s8.pdf Audi S8 (2012.10)]</ref>\n\n==== Engines ====\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable collapsible\" style=\"font-size:98%;\"\n|+Petrol engines\n!Model!!Years!!Type!!Power at rpm!!Torqu